Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐久間學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想如果在發信的同時把手機扔上天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會就有訊號 呼叫到救援呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一次也沒成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.37,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(565,248)}實里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.37,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(732,291)}爸爸：媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.37,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(556,334)}救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.37,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(519,434)}我們在密林裡 再往深處找找！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.37,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(577,583)}發送失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要進林子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好做一下標記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為很容易迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
